caption: I know there are so so many people that deserve to win this and it's so hard that only one can but I will do everything I can to try and show you why I should be considered. I have been supporting Jack and Jack for almost 2 years and the mean absolutely everything to me. I know this is cliche but they saved me, if it weren't for Jack and Jack I probably wouldn't be here now. Through the hardest times in my life Jack and Jack were always there to keep me positive and put a smile on my face. There are no words or actions to describe how much I love them. I'm spooningjacks on Twitter and Instagram and I made those to try and show my support a bit more. I should have met Jack and Jack at digifest but m&g was cancelled, it's still the worst day in my entire life, but I won't give up. I know that it's terrible but hopefully it will be worth the wait. Getting the opportunity to meet them and go to one of their shows is more than I could ever ask for. Thanking them and telling them how proud I am would mean everything. I can't express how much I want to win this and personally thank Jack and Jack for everything they've done for me. Please help me meet my idols, thank you(:❤️ #contest
